1. *Tony* je bio prvi koji je pokušao da se popne na planinu. (Tony was the first one to try to climb the mountain.)
2. Oni su sa *Tonijem* proveli prekrasan dan. (They had a wonderful day with Tony.)
3. *Toniju* je bilo veoma teško da pronađe odgovarajući posao. (It was very difficult for Tony to find a suitable job.)
4. *Toni* je radio na projektu za tri meseca. (Tony worked on the project for three months.)
5. *Tonijev* roditelji su bili vrlo ponosni na njega. (Tony's parents were very proud of him.)